@page "/volunteer"
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Volunteer Page</title>
    <!-- Link to Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html, body {
            font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
            background-image: url('images/background1.png');
            background-size: cover; /* Ensure the background image covers the entire page */
            background-attachment: fixed; /* Keeps the background image fixed during scrolling */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .centered-text {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .volunteer-container {
            padding: 20px;
            margin: auto;
            max-width: 1200px;
            background-color: rgba(20, 57, 99, 0.8); /* Semi-transparent background to blend with the image */
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .volunteer-intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .volunteer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            justify-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .volunteer-card {
            background-color: #4775A9;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

            .volunteer-card:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
                box-shadow: 0px 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
                background-color: #ffffff;
            }

            .volunteer-card img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                object-fit: cover;
            }

            .volunteer-card h4 {
                margin: 10px 0;
                font-size: 1.4em;
                color: #143963;
            }

            .volunteer-card p {
                font-size: 1em;
                color: #333;
            }

        /* Side Navbar Styles */
        .side-navbar {
            height: 100%;
            width: 0;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            background-color: #143963;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            transition: 0.5s;
            padding-top: 60px;
            z-index: 100;
            border-right: 2px solid #ffffff;
        }
            /* Remove underline from links */
            .side-navbar .nav-link {
                padding: 15px 20px;
                font-size: 1.2em;
                color: #e0f7fa;
                display: block;
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

                /* Dark blue background on hover */
                /* White text on hover */
                /* White glow effect on hover */
                .side-navbar .nav-link:hover {
                    background-color: #4775A9;
                    color: #ffffff;
                    box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ffffff;
                }

            .side-navbar .close-btn {
                position: absolute;
                top: 15px;
                right: 25px;
                font-size: 30px;
                color: #ffffff;
            }
        /* Dark blue button */
        .open-btn {
            font-size: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #143963;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            z-index: 101;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
            /* Darker blue on hover */
            .open-btn:hover {
                background-color: #0d2a4a;
            }

        .main-content {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .sticker-container {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .sticker-image {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out; /* Smooth transition for the glowing effect */
        }

            .sticker-image:hover {
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px #FF0081, 0 0 20px #FF0081, 0 0 30px #FF0081; /* Glow effect on hover */
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2 class="centered-text">Join Our Volunteer Team</h2>

    <!-- Side Navigation Bar -->
    <div id="sideNavbar" class="side-navbar">
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="close-btn" onclick="closeNav()">×</a>
        <a href="/adopt" class="nav-link">Adopt a Pet</a>
        <a href="/awareness" class="nav-link">Awareness</a>
        <a href="/donations" class="nav-link">Donations and Sponsors</a>
        <a href="/volunteer" class="nav-link">Volunteer</a>
        <a href="/gallery" class="nav-link">Gallery</a>
        <a href="/boarding" class="nav-link">Animal Boarding</a>
        <a href="/events" class="nav-link">Events</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="main-content">
        <button class="open-btn" onclick="openNav()">☰</button>
        <div class="volunteer-container">
            <div class="volunteer-intro">
                <p>The SPCA welcomes volunteers with open paws? Yup, they're always on the lookout for big-hearted humans who want to lend a paw in making a difference for us furry pals. If you're 18 or older, you can join the team solo, but if you're younger, just bring along an adult pal! Volunteering here is a blast – you get to hang out with all sorts of fluffy friends and help take care of them in a super fun environment. So, why wait? Reach out to them and offer your services today! Let's make tails wag and hearts smile together!</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Volunteer Opportunities Grid -->
            <div class="volunteer-grid">
                <div class="volunteer-card">
                    <img src="images/breadcat.jpg" alt="Animal Care" />
                    <h4>Animal Care</h4>
                    <p>Feeding, grooming, and exercising the animals.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="volunteer-card">
                    <img src="images/dogg.jpg" alt="Event Assistance" />
                    <h4>Event Assistance</h4>
                    <p>Helping organize and manage SPCA events.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="volunteer-card">
                    <img src="images/copycat.jpg" alt="Administrative Support" />
                    <h4>Administrative Support</h4>
                    <p>Assisting with office tasks and paperwork.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Sticker at the Bottom -->
            <div class="sticker-container">
                <img src="stickers/kitty1.png" alt="Cute Kitty Sticker" class="sticker-image" id="stickerImage" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function openNav() {
            document.getElementById("sideNavbar").style.width = "250px";
        }

        function closeNav() {
            document.getElementById("sideNavbar").style.width = "0";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
